.UNINDENT
.INDENT 0.0
.TP
.B \-\-wait\-for\-completion
等待所有书籍都编入索引，定期显示索引进度
.UNINDENT
.SH FTS_SEARCH
.INDENT 0.0
.INDENT 3.5
.sp
.EX
calibredb fts_search [options]  search expression
.EE
